Virtual Private Cloud
=====================


The scope of VPC is region.
An Internet Gateway(IG) is attached to a VPC
A subnet is a range of ip adress residing in VPC
To deploy resources in VPC subnet is required.
Routing table is attached to VPC to forward/accept traffic from subnets.
IG is required for forwarding traffic to the internet.
VPC end point for connecting to aws resources privately.
The scope of VPC is region(us-east-1,us-east-2,us-west-2)

Each region has number of availibility zones.
Subnets can be added to VPC after creating VPC.

Connect to aws vpc from on premise using VPN.
